additional information on these costs.
26. Subsequent event
On February 1, 2021, we acquired the Oil & Gas Division (“SPM Oil & Gas”) of the Weir Group PLC for approximately
$375 million. Headquartered near Fort Worth, Texas, SPM Oil & Gas will produce a full line of pumps, flow iron, consumable
parts, wellhead and pressure control products that are offered via an extensive global network of service centers.1 3 3 3 3
